lines.text: Take a quick survey & enter for the chance
to WIN a $250 Sprouts gift card. Go to:
"Valid 4/8/24-4/14/24 in-store in our AL, CA, DE,
GA, MD, NC, NI, PA, SC, TN, UT, VA. WA NV-Reno
calculated after applying all other coupons and
discounts and excludes amounts for tax, alcohol,
postage & gift cards. Not valid online or on prior
purchases. To use in-store scan receipt barcode.
Limit one per transaction. Cannot be combined
with other Sprouts cash-off offers or employee
discount. No cash redemption unless required by
law @ 1/100c. Void if duplicated, sold or
transferred. Subject to all applicable laws.
